    %% Root Operator Dependencies
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Dashboard
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| NotebookCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|manages| KServe
    RHODSOp -->|manages| ModelMesh
    RHODSOp -->|manages| DSP
    RHODSOp -->|manages| CodeFlare
    RHODSOp -->|manages| KubeRay
    RHODSOp -->|manages| Kueue
    RHODSOp -->|manages| TrustyAI

    %% Dashboard Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|authenticates via| OAuth
    Dashboard -->|queries metrics| Prometheus
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| OpenShift
    Dashboard -.->|optional queries| Thanos

    %% Notebook Controller Dependencies
    NotebookCtrl -->|creates Routes| Router
    NotebookCtrl -->|OAuth integration| OAuth
    NotebookCtrl -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA
    NotebookCtrl -->|deploys pods| OpenShift

    %% KServe Dependencies
    KServe -->|requires| Knative
    KServe -->|requires| Istio
    KServe -->|TLS certs| CertManager
    KServe -->|model storage| S3

    %% Model Controller Dependencies
    ModelCtrl -->|creates Routes| Router
    ModelCtrl -->|configures mesh| Istio
    ModelCtrl -->|creates ServiceMonitors| Prometheus
    ModelCtrl -->|aggregates storage secrets| OpenShift

    %% ModelMesh Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|state management| etcd
    ModelMesh -->|model storage| S3
    ModelMesh -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA
    ModelMesh -.->|optional Service Mesh| Istio

    %% Data Science Pipelines Dependencies
    DSP -->|pipeline execution| Tekton
    DSP -->|metadata storage| MariaDB
    DSP -->|artifact storage| Minio
    DSP -->|OAuth integration| OAuth
    DSP -.->|external storage| S3

    %% CodeFlare Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|manages Ray workloads| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|node autoscaling| MachineAPI
    CodeFlare -->|job admission| Kueue

    %% KubeRay Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|creates Routes| Router
    KubeRay -->|queueing integration| Kueue
    KubeRay -.->|optional fault tolerance| Redis

    %% Kueue Dependencies
    Kueue -->|watches workloads| OpenShift
    Kueue -->|integrates with| CodeFlare
    Kueue -->|integrates with| KubeRay

    %% TrustyAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|patches InferenceServices| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|patches Predictors| ModelMesh
    TrustyAI -->|creates Routes| Router
    TrustyAI -->|OAuth integration| OAuth
    TrustyAI -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus

    %% All Components to Core Infrastructure
    RHODSOp -->|API calls| OpenShift
    KServe -->|API calls| OpenShift
    ModelMesh -->|API calls| OpenShift
    DSP -->|API calls| OpenShift
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| OpenShift
    KubeRay -->|API calls| OpenShift
    Kueue -->|API calls| OpenShift
    TrustyAI -->|API calls| OpenShift

    %% Container Image Dependencies
    RHODSOp -->|pulls images| Registries
    Dashboard -->|pulls images| Registries
    NotebookCtrl -->|pulls images| Registries
    KServe -->|pulls images| Registries
    ModelMesh -->|pulls images| Registries
    DSP -->|pulls images| Registries
    KubeRay -->|pulls images| Registries
    TrustyAI -->|pulls images| Registries

    %% User Workload Dependencies (represented through operators)
    NotebookCtrl -.->|notebooks access| PyPI
    NotebookCtrl -.->|notebooks access| Git
    NotebookCtrl -.->|notebooks access| Databases
    NotebookCtrl -.->|notebooks access| S3

    %% Monitoring Integration
    Dashboard -.->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    KServe -.->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    ModelMesh -.->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    DSP -.->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    TrustyAI -.->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    Prometheus -->|sends alerts| Alertmanager

